# SlimeWire routing (Cloudflare Pages / any _redirects-aware proxy).
# gg is THE site now and IS index.html, so "/" already serves it. These map the old-app entry
# aliases onto the new app, archive the old terminal at /old (static, APIs off), and keep referral
# links working. NOTE: no /api/* rule here on purpose — the existing API proxy is left untouched.
/old            /old.html              200
/old/*          /old.html              200
/r/*            /?ref=:splat           302
/launch-coin    /#launch               302
/terminal       /index.html            200
/terminal/*     /index.html            200
/portal         /index.html            200
/portal/*       /index.html            200
/connect        /index.html            200
/login          /index.html            200
/account/login  /index.html            200
